'Aku, Purshottam,
membebaskanmu dari sumpahmu'

00:20:55.160 --> 00:20:58.120 line:20%
'mengorbankan kemewahan
gaya hidup agung ini.'

00:20:59.920 --> 00:21:04.160 line:20%
'Kau memaksa Purshottam untuk
memberi kami gaya hidup agung kami?'

00:21:04.440 --> 00:21:05.680 line:20%
